snippet.title: Octopus Goulash Trailer
snippet.description:
Explore a futuristic metropolis, interact with a population of NPCs, and experience a unique narrative. Engage in dynamic missions, battle between flying cars, and shape your story in this interactive world where every choice is an opportunity, every moment an unparalleled adventure.
www.octopusgoulash.com
https://store.steampowered.com/app/2810700/Octopus_Goulash/
